erlang-lru version 2.2.0, released on 2016/10/12
================================================

- improvements: allows a function to return `{ok, Val}`.

erlang-lru version 2.1.0, released on 2016/10/12
================================================

- add the possibility to pass a function to `lru:add/3` or `lru:contains_or_add/3 ` functions.

erlang-lru version 2.0.0, released on 2016/10/08
================================================

- add options to evict items in the cache depending on their size (in bytes)
or  number

** DEPRECATION **: `size`in 1.x should now be set using the `max_objs` setting.
